---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Services">
  <section class="relative pt-32 pb-24 sm:pb-32">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-indigo-600/5 via-deep-900 to-transparent -z-10" />
    
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-center">
        <p class="reveal visible text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-indigo-400">Services</p>
        <h1 class="reveal visible reveal-delay-1 mt-3 text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-5xl">Ce que je peux faire pour vous</h1>
        <p class="reveal visible reveal-delay-2 mt-4 text-lg text-gray-400">
          Du site vitrine à l'application complexe, je m'adapte à vos besoins et votre budget.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-20 space-y-6">
        <div class="reveal group rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-deep-800/50 p-8 sm:p-10 backdrop-blur-sm transition-all duration-300 hover:border-indigo-500/20 hover:bg-deep-800/80">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-6">
            <div class="flex h-12 w-12 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-indigo-500/10 text-indigo-400 text-sm font-bold">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 16V8a2 2 0 0 0-1-1.73l-7-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 0l-7 4A2 2 0 0 0 3 8v8a2 2 0 0 0 1 1.73l7 4a2 2 0 0 0 2 0l7-4A2 2 0 0 0 21 16z"/><polyline points="3.27 6.96 12 12.01 20.73 6.96"/><line x1="12" y1="22.08" x2="12" y2="12"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white group-hover:text-indigo-300 transition-colors">Sites WordPress</h2>
              <p class="mt-3 text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
                Thème sur mesure, WooCommerce, intégration de plugins, optimisation des performances.
                Je ne me contente pas d'installer un thème pré-fait — chaque site est pensé pour vos objectifs.
              </p>
              <ul class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                <li class="rounded-full bg-indigo-500/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs text-indigo-300">Thème sur mesure</li>
                <li class="rounded-full bg-indigo-500/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs text-indigo-300">WooCommerce</li>
                <li class="rounded-full bg-indigo-500/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs text-indigo-300">Optimisation</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-1 group rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-deep-800/50 p-8 sm:p-10 backdrop-blur-sm transition-all duration-300 hover:border-purple-500/20 hover:bg-deep-800/80">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-6">
            <div class="flex h-12 w-12 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-purple-500/10 text-purple-400 text-sm font-bold">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"/><line x1="3" y1="9" x2="21" y2="9"/><line x1="9" y1="21" x2="9" y2="9"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white group-hover:text-purple-300 transition-colors">Développement sur mesure</h2>
              <p class="mt-3 text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
                Next.js, Astro, React, Node.js. Des sites statiques ultra-rapides aux applications dynamiques.
                Stack moderne, déploiement continu via Git/Vercel, performance optimale.
              </p>
              <ul class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                <li class="rounded-full bg-purple-500/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs text-purple-300">Next.js / Astro</li>
                <li class="rounded-full bg-purple-500/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs text-purple-300">React / TypeScript</li>
                <li class="rounded-full bg-purple-500/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs text-purple-300">API & CMS headless</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-2 group rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-deep-800/50 p-8 sm:p-10 backdrop-blur-sm transition-all duration-300 hover:border-amber-500/20 hover:bg-deep-800/80">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-6">
            <div class="flex h-12 w-12 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-amber-500/10 text-amber-400 text-sm font-bold">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 20h9"/><path d="M16.5 3.5a2.121 2.121 0 0 1 3 3L7 19l-4 1 1-4L16.5 3.5z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white group-hover:text-amber-300 transition-colors">Maintenance & Évolution</h2>
              <p class="mt-3 text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
                Audit technique, corrections de sécurité, mise à jour, ajout de fonctionnalités.
                Je peux aussi reprendre un site existant et le faire passer à la vitesse supérieure.
              </p>
              <ul class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                <li class="rounded-full bg-amber-500/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs text-amber-300">Audit & Sécurité</li>
                <li class="rounded-full bg-amber-500/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs text-amber-300">Migration</li>
                <li class="rounded-full bg-amber-500/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs text-amber-300">Performance</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="relative py-24 sm:py-32">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-600/10 via-deep-900 to-purple-600/10 -z-10" />
    
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="reveal rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-600/10 to-purple-600/10 p-8 sm:p-12 backdrop-blur-sm">
        <div class="max-w-2xl">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white sm:text-3xl">Vous ne savez pas par où commencer ?</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-lg text-gray-400">
            C'est normal. On en parle 30 minutes sans engagement, je vous conseille et vous repartez avec une vision claire.
          </p>
          <a href="/contact" class="mt-6 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-600 to-purple-600 px-8 py-3.5 text-base font-semibold text-white shadow-lg shadow-indigo-500/25 transition-all duration-200 hover:shadow-indigo-500/50 hover:scale-[1.02]">
            Réserver un appel gratuit
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
